    <item>
      <title>Cloudflare 首席执行官试图避开马斯克与巴西就 X 展开的争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/cloudflare-ceo-seeks-to-steer-clear-of-musk-s-brazil-feud-over-x</link>
      <description><![CDATA[网络提供商 Cloudflare Inc 的首席执行官周一表示，该公司既没有帮助伊隆马斯克的 X 逃避巴西的禁令，也没有协助该国监管机构恢复禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/cloudflare-ceo-seeks-to-steer-clear-of-musk-s-brazil-feud-over-x</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 18:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币矿工休战为暴动接管 Bitfarms 留下可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/crypto-miner-truce-leaves-open-the-possibility-of-riot-taking-over-bitfarms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管比特币矿商 Bitfarms Ltd. 已与 Riot Platforms Inc. 就长达数月的收购纠纷达成停战协议，但该协议仍为收购留下了可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/crypto-miner-truce-leaves-open-the-possibility-of-riot-taking-over-bitfarms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 18:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Constellation 首席执行官称美国应效仿中国以满足人工智能电力使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/constellation-ceo-sees-ai-as-critical-to-us-national-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家电力公司的负责人表示，为了满足人工智能运行对电力的激增的需求，美国应该效仿中国。该公司刚刚与微软公司签署协议，重新开放已关闭的三哩岛核电站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/constellation-ceo-sees-ai-as-critical-to-us-national-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 17:28:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果股价尾盘暴跌引发外界猜测谁在抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/apple-s-late-day-plunge-stirs-speculation-over-who-was-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五本应是苹果公司股价的好日子，这家 iPhone 制造商将成为主要股指季度调整的大赢家。在大部分交易时段，情况都是如此——直到收盘前 10 分钟左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/apple-s-late-day-plunge-stirs-speculation-over-who-was-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 17:15:21 GMT</pubDate>
